indicators.questionText: How has this person grown as a teacher, professional, learner and member of your school community?
How has this teacher grown along a continuum? (refer to the Continuum of Teacher Development from the NTC@UC Santa Cruz)
What specific changes have you observed that you want to highlight and/or celebrate?
What are some questions and/or needs this teacher has expressed?
What are some possible resources and/or next steps to help support this teacher's growth?
